    PROTOCOL FOR THE PREPARATION OF COUNTRY CASE STUDIES

ON NURSING PRACTICE IN

LOCAL HEALTH SYSTEMS IN LATIN AMERICA



(Corrected version following the test)



















30 April 1992











TABLE OF CONTENTS



